1. THE HOOVER FEATURE:
instead clicking each time on a button. we did a hoover feature where the user
clicks one time on a letter, hovers the mouse over the letters he wants to
choose, and by clicking again he confirms the marked letters

2. OPENING WINDOW:
a window that pop up in the starting of a game, it has two buttons:
play button: starts a round of the game.
instructions button: description is found below.

3. CLOSING WINDOW:
a window that pop up when the time of the game is out.
has two buttons:
back to menu button: description is found below.
play again button: get the player to another game.

4. BACK TO MENU BUTTON:
gets the player back to the opening window.

5.INSTRUCTIONS BUTTON:
opens the instructions of the game.